      "description": "Proposals are checked for duplicates before submission.",
      "checks": [
        "Exact slug match against existing published terms (409)",
        "Exact slug match against open proposal issues (409)",
        "Fuzzy name similarity >85% via Dice coefficient against existing terms (409)",
